{"tid":2058060,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［危險風向］［Y not both] 彭博：與其懲罰中國，不如接收香港人","createTime":"2020-06-10T01:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T02:04:35.000Z","uid":48083,"like":20,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bfa683281da88304e4e6327570c2e53957e0fc0e","tid":2058060,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T01:16:18.000Z","msg":"A Better Way to Help Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nInstead of trying to punish China, the West should open its doors to the city&rsquo;s residents.<br />\nBy Editorial Board<br />\nJune 8, 2020, 8:00 AM EDT<br />\n<br />\n.....What's more, unlike many of the Trump administration&rsquo;s more harebrained ideas, this one doesn&rsquo;t undermine U.S. interests or depend for success on altering another country's behavior. <br />\n<br />\nAs a general rule, in the long-term competition with China, the U.S. would do better to focus on building up its own strengths rather than seeking to weaken the People&rsquo;s Republic. That means working with its allies, rebuilding its economy, and restoring its moral authority as an open and inclusive society. Welcoming immigrants from Hong Kong would do all three.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2020-06-08/u-s-should-let-hong-kong-residents-immigrate-after-security-law\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fopinion%2Farticles%2F2020-06-08%2Fu-s-should-let-hong-kong-residents-immigrate-after-security-law&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa9Rt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=bcbff5d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2020-06-08/u-s-should-let-hong-kong-residents-immigrate-after-security-law</a><br />\n<br />\n睇嚟民主黨可能想以接受香港人嚟交功課<br />\n做為放生支共既借口"},{"pid":"f9bc6497502a2ac2a394c0c2849b7435dc002b3c","tid":2058060,"uid":56698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T01:17:59.000Z","msg":"民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />